name: TraitOSE the first version
description:
TraisOSE is a emulator of a OS like windows.

This is the very first version of TraitOSE. (TraitOSE v.0.00.01). You can find a lot more info about this on the TraitOSE wiki: https://sites.google.com/view/traitose-wiki/first-version 

To play it you have to download all the files. To open it, open the ".exe" file. 

To go though the menus, you use the F keys, like F1 and F2.

Programs that's are included are: info, internet, files, physics sim1, walk3D, race3D, and code.

If you have a question put it on the discussion board below.
